import tkinter as tk

import base64

import io

from PIL import Image, ImageTk

import random

import sys

import os

import pygame

import threading

class BouncingPopup:

def __init__(self, root, embedded_image, screen_width, screen_height):

self.popup = tk.Toplevel(root)

self.popup.title(" ")

decoded_image = base64.b64decode(embedded_image)

self.image = Image.open(io.BytesIO(decoded_image))

self.photo = ImageTk.PhotoImage(self.image)

self.label = tk.Label(self.popup, image=self.photo)

self.label.pack()

self.popup.geometry(f"{self.image.width}x{self.image.height}")

self.x = random.randint(0, screen_width - self.image.width)

self.y = random.randint(0, screen_height - self.image.height)

self.popup.geometry(f"+{self.x}+{self.y}")

self.dx = random.choice([-2, 2])

self.dy = random.choice([-2, 2])

self.screen_width = screen_width

self.screen_height = screen_height

self.move_popup()

self.popup.protocol("WM_DELETE_WINDOW", self.on_close)

def move_popup(self):

self.x += self.dx

self.y += self.dy

if self.x < 0 or self.x + self.image.width > self.screen_width:

self.dx = -self.dx

if self.y < 0 or self.y + self.image.height > self.screen_height:

self.dy = -self.dy

self.popup.geometry(f"+{self.x}+{self.y}")

self.popup.after(20, self.move_popup)

def on_close(self):

self.popup.destroy()

os.system('python {}'.format(os.path.abspath(__file__)))

sys.exit()

def play_base64_audio(base64_audio_data, file_format='mp3'):

audio_data = base64.b64decode(base64_audio_data)

audio_file_like = io.BytesIO(audio_data)

pygame.mixer.init()

pygame.mixer.music.load(audio_file_like, file_format)

pygame.mixer.music.play()

while pygame.mixer.music.get_busy():

pygame.time.Clock().tick(10)

def play_audio_in_thread(embedded_audio):

audio_thread = threading.Thread(target=play_base64_audio, args=(embedded_audio,))

audio_thread.start()

def create_multiple_popups(embedded_image, num_popups):

root = tk.Tk()

root.withdraw()

screen_width = root.winfo_screenwidth()

screen_height = root.winfo_screenheight()

popups = [BouncingPopup(root, embedded_image, screen_width, screen_height) for _ in range(num_popups)]

play_audio_in_thread(embedded_audio)

root.mainloop()
